Reformulated Description in English

I need to understand why this bug is appearing and how to resolve it.
When a user tries to reschedule a service appointment, the system displays an error message and does not allow saving the new appointment time.

Steps to Reproduce the Bug

1. Open this link: [link from the screenshot]


2. Go to the external appointment booking portal.


3. Select one of the available service appointments.


4. Change the appointment date and/or time (for example, set the scheduled date to 12/12/2025).


5. Choose any time slot and click Save.


6. The system displays the following error message (shown in the screenshot):
FS1_ERROR: "Service Appointment update caused by Connected Field Service failed. This feature is not currently enabled for this user."
